{"tid":519373,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[痴線佬籌款] 2017 走到香港的盡頭 - 環繞香港行一圈回憶錄","createTime":"2018-01-04T09:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T04:53:09.000Z","uid":82002,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00300c2b50437fdeb52395453f2c5b1c50c81a0b","tid":519373,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:32:14.000Z","msg":"講左路線先：<br />\nDay 1 (27/5/2017) : 55公里 香港島繞一圈 （會展 - 銅鑼灣 - 北角 - 鰂魚涌 - 大潭郊野公園 - 孖桿山 - 赤柱 - 淺水灣 - 黃竹坑 - 香港仔 - 薄扶林 - 香港大學 - 太平山頂 - 中環碼頭）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SR4u7J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSR4u7J0.jpg&h=74bf339b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 2 (30/5/2017) : 64公里 寶琳到元朗 （寶琳 - 秀茂坪 - 觀塘 - 九龍灣 - 九龍城 - 九龍塘 - 深水埗 - 荔枝角 - 青山公路 - 荃灣 - 汀九橋 - 青山公路 - 黃金海岸 - 屯門市中心 - 洪水橋 - 元朗）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2RUts9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2RUts9a.jpg&h=d0e709f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 3 (2/6/2017) : 54公里 上水到彩虹（上水 - 粉嶺 - 太和 - 大埔 - 科學園 - 沙田 - 馬鞍山 - 烏溪沙 - 西貢 - 彩虹）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TYQ9vUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTYQ9vUQ.jpg&h=8458f7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登一向多痴線佬，小弟都唔例外。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一向鍾意行路跑步強身健體既我，<br />\n舊年sem break（五月尾六月頭）<br />\n有日行下行下就唸：<br />\n步行籌款聽得多，<br />\n如果自己搞個環香港一圈既步行籌款，<br />\n拖幾個兄弟落水，<br />\n究竟又會唔會成功籌錢幫到人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n橫掂又得閒到死，一於就去馬，<br />\n於是果日返屋企就即刻打開個google map plan 路程，<br />\n又周圍問有無癡線佬朋友一齊玩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果陣日日三十幾度，要行曬成個香港<br />\n加埋接近180公里既路程，D人啋你都傻啦。<br />\n但古語有云：有志者鄧竟成，<br />\n精誠所至就腿張開。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我費盡口舌，竟然又比我揾到六七個人一齊陪我癲！<br />\n一個人做痴線野叫做發癲，<br />\n但一堆人做痴線野就夠堅，<br />\n多撚謝曬你地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老土D都講句，如果無你地支撐住，<br />\n我第一日未入到赤柱都已經爛尾！<br />\n<br />\n然後就響Facebook籌款，<br />\n呢次收番黎既錢會全數捐比無國界醫生，<br />\n買水飲啊，車費啊全部都唔會扣。<br />\n以為無咩人理，<br />\n點知可能Google Map plot 出黎果幾幅路線圖太驚嚇，<br />\nD 人竟然勁踴躍捐錢，最後都籌到3,500蚊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n據無國界個Staff講呢筆錢<br />\n足夠為五百個非洲人提供八個月的醫療費用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真假唔知，可能作大，但有好過無，<br />\n所以多謝埋所有捐左錢既善長仁翁 （如果你地有睇呢個Post）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cV0VCMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcV0VCMZ.jpg&h=d9403b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/J46azfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJ46azfU.jpg&h=77d38f9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97a0994acb5ffa387a1d1f7f48e609ed297e9122","tid":519373,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"比少少相大家睇下當Preview先，其實今次其中一樣最難忘既就係：香港真係好撚靚，D人講要自己發掘靚景，老套得黎原來係真。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AKeNO0M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAKeNO0M.jpg&h=db22b535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n漫無止境既青山公路，引無數英雄競折腰<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bgmzFUX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbgmzFUX.jpg&h=03e68436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sn0dsHn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fsn0dsHn.jpg&h=b16d514b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翻過孖崗山，赤柱景色攝人心脾<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KkXw8Cq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKkXw8Cq.jpg&h=6c1341eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曬到傻既九龍東<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PnKKsug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPnKKsug.jpg&h=80e56e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夕陽斜暉，灑滿黃竹坑大馬路<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yc0XIiu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fyc0XIiu.jpg&h=cd8c9b19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e404e38af0781d1ab4d6099fd3f11e8b217dc69","tid":519373,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zo3XoC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fzo3XoC4.jpg&h=ec626c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月27號，三十度。<br />\n第一日，五個癲佬興高采烈出發。<br />\n我，得仔，老狗，迪迪，艇佬。<br />\n我負責行程，同埋行；<br />\n老狗負責free ride，負責笑；<br />\n迪迪專門擒高擒低影相；<br />\n得仔同艇佬多行山經驗，行山路負責帶方向。<br />\n呢五條友入面，最後只有三個人可以行曬三日全程。<br />\n<br />\n九點相約灣仔碼頭，仲係好興奮好撚期待<br />\n真係無知者無畏，少年，你們太年輕了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NBHxExy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNBHxExy.jpg&h=3f8d3c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n起步點係金紫荊廣場，無咩特別意義，<br />\n唔通貪果度夠多強國人咩？<br />\n迪迪好撚鍾意影相，<br />\n真係揾左個強國人，<br />\n走過去講 &ldquo;send 身，棒手拍蕉可以嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有比強國人渣機影相都應該知<br />\n強國人好鍾意叫你擺Pose果陣講 [茄子]。<br />\n但今次呢個強國人就別出心裁，爆左句 [香港美不美？ ]<br />\n我地Dead air左三秒，條友又問多次，<br />\n[怎麼了？香港美不美？ ]<br />\n原來expect我地答 [美] 跟住個嘴就會好似大笑緊咁。<br />\n咁都比你撚到，真係抵你做強國人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3mo8nS3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3mo8nS3.jpg&h=43b37009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係旅程既開始。<br />\n宜家笑下好啦，之後就係煉獄既開始。"},{"pid":"9936210a7134868cbe1cfb6fd50c6404f23cde72","tid":519373,"uid":71425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"231eb648e87f171fbe1cc79203a84539f46bd377","tid":519373,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"Pishh<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8ac766a9d3e27e0f6b33c02d98d135533101bb","tid":519373,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:55:09.000Z","msg":"等你出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜身邊無痴線佬 無人肯陪我癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1f6b601fcd09de1df4db13eb6f2f244837d350","tid":519373,"uid":53758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:46:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dec71c41cea6417826c82c2b3ab89b65d3ba916","tid":519373,"uid":11960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T19:43:32.000Z","msg":"hello <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa1c081c528a4dae2748b4d622d50019d76f02c","tid":519373,"uid":109961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T20:13:53.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad783dd4fc02923bb31f9025658c51cce9d5a9e0","tid":519373,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zI0qP9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzI0qP9k.jpg&h=05c5ea0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就昂然踏著前路去啦。<br />\n九點半金紫荊出發，<br />\n首先會行渣打馬拉松去維園果條路先，<br />\n然後再響天后直接鏟入去北角。<br />\n本身行程我地打算由石澳行入赤柱，<br />\n但得仔同艇佬就話：既然都係行就不如行山啦！<br />\n於是我地決定去十一點到鰂魚湧後<br />\n會取道柏架山道入大潭，<br />\n再翻過孖桿山，目標三點可以入到赤柱食番個下午茶。<br />\n我地打算維持五公里每小時既步速，<br />\n十二個鐘頭，即係夜晚十點前<br />\n點都去到中環碼頭啦掛？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tujDk1w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtujDk1w.jpg&h=dc3341da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n灣仔運動場對出，路路暢通。<br />\n大家仲有講有笑，眉飛色舞。<br />\n老狗（藍色衫）另轉身同揸機既迪迪講：<br />\n行快D啦咪撚掛住影相。<br />\n好彩迪迪無聽佢講，<br />\n之後仲影得更加變本加厲，<br />\n成個旅程先有咁多珍貴既回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/M5mMeHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FM5mMeHa.jpg&h=93f6c11e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬師道天橋，一條令馬拉松跑手聞之色變既賽道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vRD1FFy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvRD1FFy.jpg&h=b6ce0ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就轉落去銅鑼灣，<br />\n直入去就係維園。<br />\n到到呢度，大家都輕輕鬆松，步速維持得好快。"},{"pid":"8bfaebbf69d5d49ec38cfbef714f9ba815725acc","tid":519373,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LYdg7oX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLYdg7oX.jpg&h=a2d95f46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n維園一出無幾耐就係興發街，<br />\n我地想keep住睇到個海，<br />\n所以就無行英皇道。<br />\n十分鐘前先響繁華擁擠既銅鑼灣穿過黎，<br />\n十分鐘後就入到唐樓林立，古樸厚實既天后北角。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0I0kwcl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0I0kwcl.jpg&h=9a2a8173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行到砲台山，經過呢一棟紅磚建築，<br />\n同附近既唐樓電車一對比，<br />\n有一種奢華而古典既感覺。<br />\n迪迪個on9仲特登跳過去對面馬路<br />\n趁無車經過幫我地影左呢幅相。<br />\n有無人可以話我知呢棟野係乜？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uwF8pjl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuwF8pjl.jpg&h=c6fbcb63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後入到渣華道，<br />\n平時聽電視電台聽得多呢個名，<br />\n但大家都真係第一次黎。<br />\n下面果間上海理髮鋪個樣咁舊，<br />\n唔知又有無巴打係果度剪過頭髮呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oeDLeKN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoeDLeKN.jpg&h=ebbb388c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行行下見到間馬會，<br />\n上面痴住小弟既愛駒明月千里，<br />\n果陣因為就快跑遮打杯，<br />\n小弟指住祝佢旗開得勝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nz1FjdZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fnz1FjdZ.jpg&h=ef372d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後話咁快就去到鰂魚涌，<br />\n其實大約都只係行左一個鐘多D，<br />\n得仔就話著名既港女IG聖地巨廈就係隔離，<br />\n不如入去影下MK相。<br />\n之後再去隔離個體育館放下水，<br />\n就直上柏架山道，<br />\n穿越大潭直達港島既最南端！"},{"pid":"87e4de7e5dd739f666c1a94e7956ce7963c2c1e2","tid":519373,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}